childContentItems.displayName:
Tellem is an app that connects customers to businesses.

Our immediate focus is to provide a mobile application for customer feedback.

Tellem IS:
  • A quick and easy way for consumers to provide feedback direct to a business.
  • A new contact point for business seeking ways to improve their service offering
Tellem is NOT:
  • Social media – we send feedback from customers direct to businesses, not published on sites such as Facebook or Twitter
  • A Survey – We employ a one-page-only approach. Tell’em then move on.
